**Key decision rationale:**

Redis Streams wins because it fits your constraints:
- **Time**: <1 week setup using existing Redis (vs >2 weeks for Kafka)
- **Team**: Leverages existing Redis knowledge (vs zero Kafka experience)
- **Budget**: No additional infrastructure costs (vs managed Confluent Cloud unaffordable)
